The HQLI-1 customer, John Brett identified two 
issues in the system: 
One: There is a problem with the Line Item Query screen:    Notice a specific project is selected and filtered on ADJ GL and Procurement  (SS1).  When you select the line it  takes you to the GL process, not the ADJ GL. (SS2).     When you select  Back to HQLI List  (SS2), it takes you all the way out (SS3).  It should take you to SS1.
Two:  Running the ?By Project?  Guideline report in Excel gives the  ?By Line? Item version instead.
